                            imagePosition="top"
                            text="&lt;p>The Platform module in combination with the 'Pages' module are providing a 'in place' staging&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>Request routing for public and editing requests&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/system/console/configMgr&quot; title=&quot;OSGI configuration for the platform services&quot; target=&quot;osgi&quot;>Access restriction&lt;/a> according to the access mode (public or author)&lt;/li>&lt;li>Release management in the 'Pages' module&lt;/li>&lt;li>Content delivery for releases&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>&lt;p>&lt;/p>"
