                            imagePosition="top"
                            text="&lt;p>The Composum Console is the low level layer to manipulate content and develop components in the repository.&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/browser.html/content/sites&quot; title=&quot;JCR Browser feature of the Composum Console&quot; target=&quot;console&quot;>JCR Browser&lt;/a>&lt;br>walk through the whole repository, edit nodes, properties, files and test the rendering results&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/packages.html/backup/content&quot; title=&quot;Package Manager feature of the Composum Console&quot; target=&quot;console&quot;>Package Manager&lt;/a>&lt;br>organize your modules and content in packages and define your backup artifacts as packages&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/users.html/home/users/tenants/IST/rw&quot; title=&quot;User Manager feature of the Composum Console&quot; target=&quot;console&quot;>User Manager&lt;/a>&lt;br>for group and user administration; ACL manipulation is integrated in the JCR Browser&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>&lt;p>&lt;/p>"
                            textAlignment="left"
                            title="Console">
