                    <textimage-01
                            jcr:primaryType="cpp:Element"
                            sling:resourceType="composum/pages/components/element/textimage"
                            imagePosition="top"
                            text="&lt;p>Pages is the brand new module which provides a CMS UI to manipulate your content in an intuitive way. the content is organized in&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/pages.html/content/ist/composum&quot; title=&quot;go to this site in the 'Pages' UI&quot; target=&quot;pages&quot;>Sites&lt;/a>&lt;br>the managing entry point to one site on the platform which contains all pages and assets and declares the releases, languages and mapping rules for the internet site&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/pages.html/content/ist/composum/home/slides&quot; title=&quot;go tho this pages in the 'Pages' UI&quot; target=&quot;pages&quot;>Pages&lt;/a>&lt;br>the versioned content of a site is structured in a hierarchy of pages&lt;/li>&lt;li>Containers&lt;br>are arranging sets of elements e.g. paragraph systems element lists, slideshows, accordions, ...&lt;/li>&lt;li>Elements&lt;br>are more or less complex components without the ability to arrange elements within&lt;/li>&lt;li>Components&lt;br>the known Sling components referenced by pages, containers and elements as the resource types&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>"
                            textAlignment="left"
                            title="'Pages'">
