                            imagePosition="top"
                            text="&lt;p>The 'Assets' feature is a prototype for asset management and delivery in various resolutions.&lt;/p>&lt;p>&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>only one asset (image) source&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/browser.html/content/prototype/composum/assets/site-3/pages/image-03a&quot; title=&quot;Adaptive Image Example&quot; target=&quot;console&quot;>preconfigured variations&lt;/a> according to the design rules&lt;/li>&lt;li>&lt;a href=&quot;https://test.ist-software.com/bin/browser.html/content/prototype/composum/assets/site-3/jcr%3Acontent/assetconfig/wide&quot; target=&quot;console&quot;>generated renditions&lt;/a> for preconfigured resolutions&lt;/li>&lt;li>components for image handling an delivery&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>&lt;p>&lt;/p>"
